com.bobman159.rundml.core.model.mapping

Class FieldMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bobman159.rundml.core.model.mapping.FieldMap

  • public class FieldMap
extends java.lang.Object
    A map of class fields for mapping to a table column name using a string key (column name) that is not case sensitive. Key and Value types are expected as Strings for this class. Only the HashMap functions needed for storage of the fields mapping information are defined example 
     
	CaseInsensitiveFieldsMap<String,String> map = new FieldsMap<String,String>();
	map.put("columnName","nameColumn");
